### Success case: Valid transaction

POST localhost:8085/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromName": "Alice Smith",
  "fromIban": "DE89370400440532013000",
  "toName": "Bob Johnson",
  "toIban": "FR1420041010050500013M02606",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Payment for services"
}

### Failure case: Negative amount

POST localhost:8085/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromName": "Alice Smith",
  "fromIban": "DE89370400440532013000",
  "toName": "Bob Johnson",
  "toIban": "FR1420041010050500013M02606",
  "amount": -100.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "description": "Payment for services"
}

